node.text: Hands on with iOS 15 now live, link in profile. A consideration and commentary on over 300 features over the course of a couple of hours. This video includes a hands-on demo of SharePlay in action, among other things. Some of the accessibility features are most impressive, and some of the updates to Safari are polarizing. This really is a massive update for the iPhone. I’ll have much more commentary on individual apps and features over the course of 2021. Thanks for watching. #ios15 #iphone
